{"tid":300404,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"網上買二手器材真係好易中伏","createTime":"2017-06-28T01:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T11:19:44.000Z","uid":39137,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f6c226aa556628592ce904a9de7a2c7610272d","tid":300404,"uid":39137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:07:40.000Z","msg":"早兩日想係肥花買罪大機<br />\n個樣係好粗用都話9成新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢機身仲有有咩問題<br />\n佢竟然答冇 因為早兩日先做完保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估上架驗車咩<br />\n無啦啦拎去保養 即刻唔敢買<br />\n<br />\n事後睇返應該有人買左<br />\n但冇成交紀錄反而係已撤回<br />\n感覺成件事鬼鬼地"},{"pid":"7823881cec4800eb1bb30a6429c9b8dcf838b351","tid":300404,"uid":42753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"係有事既話個賣家點都俾人搵到架啦"},{"pid":"d253bfb6f7122c65baad4dbdac0f47d9285a850e","tid":300404,"uid":9907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"你都未買，又未check過，點知人地有伏？撤走有好多原因既，網上又唔係得肥花呢個二手網。二手野外觀點都無可能極新淨，最緊要係work。"},{"pid":"b31f4089ecacb8ca861e95e9ae351dd1d3e49558","tid":300404,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"肥花有咩野唔係九成新？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四十幾年前相機經歷N手都先至係九成新之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a419ad3ab4ea514396a214fab9935003ecf7a7d1","tid":300404,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"冇成交紀錄唔出奇<br />\n好多人交收完唔會確認"},{"pid":"5f9ed542782cf87604230fa36ba2b0eb665fc03a","tid":300404,"uid":105598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"應該話唔係淨係得一個網賣二手野<br />\nBtw 通常肥花果d 8成新已經係殘<br />\n睇相自己判斷"},{"pid":"ad2e6aadaa6cc511ec092cb655c15f7fe7b66049","tid":300404,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"之前